snippet.title: FART KING Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3630870/ 
Fart King is a hardcore platformer where every jump is a test of skill, and every mistake sends you plummeting back down. Jump by precisely controlling your fart and reach the top of the mountain to become the Fart King.  Can you control your toots well enough to reach the top?
